I want to study social work to help children who have been hurt or neglected. I also want to help families in trouble. I believe in three important values: serving others, showing respect, and acting honestly. These values are important for all social workers, and they are also important to me.

I have always wanted to help others, but I did not know what job I wanted to do. While I was in high school and college, I saw many people ignoring their problems. Some people used bad ways to deal with their problems. Because of what I saw, I decided to study psychology. I still did not know what job I wanted, so I took a break after I finished college. One summer, a friend introduced me to a 16-year-old boy who was very nervous. He was there because his parents were being mean to him. I called the police and told them I had studied psychology in college. They asked me to talk to the parents. When I asked them about the boy, they seemed nervous and made excuses. After that, I decided to study social work to help children like the boy.

Another important value is fairness. We say that every person is important, but we do not always act that way. We say we value individuality, but we often do what others do. I do not like to do what others do. I like to be myself. In high school and college, I stood up against unfairness whenever I could. I wore clothes that were not like what others wore. I protested against racism and unfairness when I saw it. I believe in fairness, and I will continue to stand up for what I believe in.

This paper looks at the Biological and Sociocultural models in relation to the sleep disorder insomnia. The Biological model focuses on genetic information and medical health issues. The Sociocultural model looks at how environment and social factors affect sleep. This review will examine research on these models and explain each study. We will look at the strengths and weaknesses of each study to better understand the models.

There are different types of sleep disorders. Some are primary sleep disorders. Others are related to mental or medical problems. Primary sleep disorders are Dyssonmias or Parasomnias. Sleep disorders related to a mental disorder are linked to a major mental illness. Other sleep disorders are caused by medical problems or a person's behavior.

Dyssonmias are sleep disorders that affect how we sleep. Some Dyssonmias are: Primary Insomnia, Primary Hypersomnia, Narcolepsy, Breathing-Related Sleep Disorder, Circadian Rhythm Sleep Disorder, and Dyssomnia Not Otherwise Specified. Primary Insomnia is a problem with sleeping too little. Primary Hypersomnia is a problem with sleeping too much. Narcolepsy causes people to fall asleep suddenly. Dyssonmias are about falling asleep and staying asleep.

Parasomnias are sleep disorders that cause behavioral problems or physical reactions. Parasomnias include Nightmare Disorder, Sleep Terror Disorder, Sleepwalking Disorder, and Parasomnias Not Otherwise Specified. Sleep disorders related to a mental illness are linked to an Axis I (serious mental illness) or Axis II (personality disorder or mental disability) disorder.

This review will focus on insomnia and primary sleep disorders. It will look at the Biological and Sociocultural models.

The Biological model of sleep disorders looks at genetic factors, hereditary traits, and physical aspects of sleep. A study on mice found that neurons in the hypothalamus that contain orexin control sleep and wakefulness. The study found that mice with a specific receptor on these neurons had problems with sleep and wake states. Researchers found that a chemical (baclofen) that activated the receptor helped mice sleep. This study suggests that there may be a genetic and environmental basis for sleep problems in humans. This could affect a person's ability to sleep without medicine.

The Sociocultural implication of this study is that if the receptor is inherited, it could affect a person's sleep. This could impact daily life, such as school, work, or other tasks that require concentration.

This paper talks about Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). First, we explain what the disorder is. Next, we explain how to diagnose it. Finally, we talk about how a teacher can help a student with CAPD in a regular classroom.

CAPD is a problem where the brain does not work correctly with sounds. People with CAPD can hear normally. They do not have a hearing problem. But their brain cannot separate sounds or understand speech in noisy places. This is not the same as being deaf or hard of hearing.

The study of CAPD began in the 1950s. Researchers were trying to understand children with speech and hearing problems. They made tests to help them. A doctor named Kimura created a way to test how the brain works with sounds in the 1960s.

CAPD can cause many problems. A person with CAPD may have trouble hearing where sounds come from. They may have trouble telling two sounds apart. They may not be able to recognize patterns in sounds. They may have trouble understanding speech. They may not be able to hear one sound because of another sound. They may not be able to understand what sounds mean.

To diagnose CAPD, a doctor must test the person with CAPD. The doctor may use questionnaires, observe how the person behaves, or use special tests. These tests can check how the person hears and responds to sounds. There is no one test that works for everyone. But doctors use many different tests to try to understand what is happening.

A teacher can help a student with CAPD in a regular classroom. First, the teacher should sit near the student. This way, the student can see the teacher's face and hear them more easily. The teacher should also avoid background noise. This can make it harder for the student to hear. The teacher should speak clearly and loudly, but not too loudly. The teacher should also give the student extra time to answer questions. This can help the student understand what is being said.

The play Twelfth Night shows that using a disguise can help people trick others. But, it can also cause problems. If a person stays in disguise too long, they may lose their true self. Ending a deception can be hard because it may hurt relationships.

The play is especially interesting when it talks about people changing their gender. This raises many questions. Why do people want to disguise themselves as the opposite sex? In the play, a character named Viola wants to change her sex to protect herself. She is a woman who is alone in a new place. She decides to pretend to be a man so she can be safe.

Viola's plan works. But it also separates her from other women. She is good at acting like a man that others start to think she is really a man. Another character, Olivia, falls in love with Viola but does not know she is a woman. Viola also has feelings for a man named Orsino but is pretending to be a man so she cannot be honest about her feelings.

The play may show that people can use a disguise to discover hidden feelings. Two characters, Olivia and Orsino, may have feelings for each other that they do not express openly. When Viola appears as a man, they are forced to think about their feelings. But, it is not clear if Olivia really likes Viola or just likes the way Viola looks. The play may be saying that people make judgments based on how others look.

This is shown when Olivia quickly switches her love from Viola to Viola's twin brother, Sebastian. She starts to see Viola as a sister rather than a love interest. The play is saying that people may not be honest about their feelings and may judge others based on how they look.

German rule in Africa was very bad. One example is the killing of the Ovaherero and Nama peoples in German South West Africa. But German rule was not the same everywhere. Each colony had its own ideas and ways of doing things. Schools in the colonies were also different. When the British took control of German East Africa (now known as Tanganyika) in 1919, they found many Africans who could read and write. Germans had also built good schools in Kamerun and other colonies.

But the situation in South West Africa (now Namibia) was different. In East Africa, the government built schools and helped teach the local people. In South West Africa, the government left most of the teaching to missionaries. The government did give some money to the missionaries, but not enough. The government, however, built many schools for Europeans living in the colony. They also controlled and supported the schools run by missionaries. This policy had a big effect on South West Africa even after German rule ended. Many Africans in South West Africa did not learn to read and write.

Other German colonies had many educated and literate Africans. But in South West Africa, “most of the people were not educated, not literate.” Many things caused this difference. This paper wants to discuss these things and look at how the people who ruled the colony and the settlers felt about the local people.

There is a lot of information about education in the German colonies. Most of this information is in German and was written a long time ago. Some of these writings describe the schools in the colonies. Later writings compared the schools in different colonies and looked at specific parts of the education system. These studies showed that the schools in each colony were different. One important study was done by Cohen. He compared the schools in South West Africa and East Africa. He said that the large number of settlers in South West Africa helped create the differences in the education system there.

South West Africa had a good climate, but much of it was desert. The number of European settlers in the colony was small compared to the population of East Africa. By 1913, about 15,000 Europeans lived in South West Africa. Only 5,336 Europeans lived in East Africa.

The music called Popular Music has grown over the past 100 years. It has many kinds. It is hard to list them all. Many kinds of music have smaller kinds. For example, the kind called Heavy Metal rock has many smaller kinds. Heavy Metal rock is expressive. It shows a wide range of feelings. It is mostly on the darker side. 

Heavy Metal rock is also very diverse. Many people started to make their own smaller kinds of Heavy Metal rock. This continued for many years. Today, there are many kinds of Heavy Metal music. It is hard to say what exactly Heavy Metal is. It has taken parts from other kinds of music. But it started from somewhere. To understand the kind of music we have today, we need to know what Heavy Metal is and why it is a movement.

Heavy Metal is a movement that is often about things that are dark. It is often loud and violent. It can be very theatrical. People who make Heavy Metal music are very good at their instruments. Heavy Metal music often comes from using strong drugs. There was a time when many people were using strong drugs. This led to music that was very strange and new. Many later kinds of Heavy Metal music took parts from the dark and exciting qualities of old music. Some songs, like Helter Skelter, show the darker side of music. This song is from the Beatles. It is considered one of the first Heavy Metal songs. It was made because the Beatles wanted to show that they could make music that was as heavy as the Rolling Stones.

Henri Rousseau was a famous artist. He painted many pictures. One of his most famous works is called The Dream. It was painted in 1910.

The Dream is more than just a picture of a woman in a dream. It shows Rousseau's own dreams and goals. He wanted to be a great artist. He wanted people to like his work.

Rousseau had a big problem. He wanted to be accepted by other artists. But he also wanted to be his own person. He wanted to paint in his own way, not like others. This made him very unhappy.

To understand The Dream, we need to know a little about Rousseau's life. He was born in 1844 in a small town in France. His father was a worker. Rousseau had no special training in art. He worked as a toll collector. At home, he had a daughter and a lot of grief. He started painting to make himself happy.

Rousseau wanted to be like other artists. He saw them painting beautiful pictures. He wanted to be good too. But Rousseau's paintings were different. He painted simple things, like the world around him. He was a folk painter.

Rousseau wanted to be famous. He wanted people to like his art. But it was hard. Many other artists were famous. They had been painting for a long time. Rousseau was older when he started. He didn't get famous until later.

A man named Jan Gordon wrote about Rousseau and another artist named Matisse. Matisse was a good painter. He didn't want to paint like others. He wanted to be different. Rousseau wanted to be like everyone else. He wanted to be accepted.

Rousseau's story is an example of a person who wanted to be accepted by others. But he also wanted to be himself. It's a big problem to solve.

Many great thinkers have suggested a strong connection between ethics and beauty. They believe that at a basic level, there is a reason for this connection. John Keats wrote in his poem "Ode on a Grecian Urn", "Beauty is truth, truth beauty - That is all / Ye know on earth, and all ye need to know." Much of what we know in life comes from education or experience. However, we seem to like ethics and beauty without being taught these things in school. Both ethics and beauty are attempts to describe, not tell us what to do. Our studies of morality and beauty are attempts to explain why something is beautiful or why an action is right, rather than a set of rules.

In fact, we cannot fully understand what is good or beautiful by just talking about it. For example, a conversation about the Mona Lisa by da Vinci may talk about its background, foreground, and contrast. But these things do not explain why it is a good piece of art. When we like a work of art or literature, we often say, "There's just something about it." I think both art and morals cannot be fully explained. As Flannery O'Connor said, "A story is a way to say something that can't be said any other way." No matter how much we describe a work of literature, there is something more.

I think ethics and art are similar because we experience both most strongly in a way that cannot be fully explained. This is true, especially for literature. As McKean said, "Literature has a moral quality that is unique. It is connected to our values in life." We need values to live. Literature is important because it gives us values.

Germany is a strong country today. It has a unique culture that comes from many different groups and tribes. The culture can be seen in many parts of the country, from the Alps in München to the city of Kiel on the Baltic Sea. It can also be seen in Köln on the Rhine River, in the center of Germany, and in the Saxon city of Dresden on the Elbe River.

Germany's culture is special because it has a long history. Many different groups lived in the area that is now Germany. The country's name, Germania, comes from the Germanic tribes. But where the name came from is not clear. Some historians think it came from a tribe known as the Tungrians. They were a group of people who lived in the area before they moved across the Rhine River and fought with the Gauls.

Julius Caesar wrote about the Germans in his book about the Gallic Wars. He used the word "Germanus" to describe the people he was fighting against. Caesar learned the word from the Gauls themselves. They used it to describe their neighbors. Caesar used the word to show the difference between the Gauls and the Germans.

The origin of the word "German" is not clear. Some people think it came from the spear that the Germanic tribes used in battle. Others think it came from the Old Irish word "garim," which means "to shout." This might mean that the Germans were loud and noisy.

The Roman historian Tacitus wrote about the Germans in his book. He said that the Germans were a separate group of people who did not mix with other groups. They lived in a wild and cold country, and they were not interested in leaving their homes to go to other places.

For a long time, the Romans did not conquer Germany. They did not want to live there. Instead, they would send soldiers to the area to get goods and to trade with the Germanic tribes. The Germanic tribes would often serve in the Roman army, and they would bring their skills back to their own homes.

I stared down at the bowl in front of me. My mind was empty. I was not thinking about the picture in front of me. I was just looking at it.

When I was a child, I wanted to learn how to draw. I bought a book called "The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain." It teaches how to understand art. One way it teaches is to use a square frame around a picture. This helps you see the picture clearly.

But at that moment, I could not think about a frame. The bowl was too busy and complicated. I was amazed by it.

I wanted to be an artist. Picasso liked blue, Monet liked green, and the Renaissance masters liked many colors. I thought the bowl could be my painting, my story, called "Work in Brown."

I picked up my pencil. My hand moved, and my mind made something new. Water was flowing, and things were moving away. But then my hand hit the toilet handle again. The brown package would not move. It was stuck.

I was unhappy. I had a mop in my hand and a green tie around my neck. I looked at the dirty package and thought about the people who clean the bathrooms at Rite Aid. I wanted to make it go away.

I flushed the toilet again. Then I used toilet paper to fix my hand. I bent down to get the package. My hand went into the water like a mother cooking a turkey.

Teenagers are dying in car accidents. Several things make this a big problem for young American drivers. The National Institutes of Health say one reason is that the teen brain is not ready for the dangers of driving. Young drivers also do not have much experience. This lack of experience causes more accidents and makes them drive too fast or drive off the road.

Teenagers also drive badly when they have friends in the car. A study in California found that when the young passenger is older, there are more car accidents.

Some states try to make driving safer for teens by requiring temporary licenses that limit the hours they can drive and say they cannot have other young people in the car.

But some people think that is not enough. They say teens are not ready to drive safely. A psychologist says that even 18 is too young to drive. He says young people like to take risks for fun. This means we should wait until they are older before they can drive. If we let young teens drive, many more people will be hurt or killed.

We can make a law to solve this problem. Schools can teach people how to drive, but no one under 18 can drive a car. A special permit can still be given before a full license, and young drivers must practice driving with an adult for a certain number of hours. This way, we can protect young drivers across the country.

This idea is not new. It is a way to keep young people safe.

I looked through the Library of Congress's library of early Edison films. I decided to watch all the trick films. There were fifteen of them from 1895 to 1901. These films use creative editing to make illusions. My study of the films focused on the way they were made and looked at the differences between most of the films and a few that were different.

Most of the trick films from the time period are made in a box on a stage. The camera does not move to follow people or objects. This way of making films came from the theater and magic shows. It has some limitations. For example, people in the films can only move side to side. They do not walk towards or away from the camera.

In the film "Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel" (1900), the actors enter from one side and move back and forth. Even when they go out of the frame, the camera does not follow them.

Most of the trick films from Edison are long shots. Sometimes they are medium shots. Close-up shots are never used. This is because of the way the films were made for the stage and theater. The actors do not move towards the camera, so close-ups are not needed.

Most of the early trick films are short. They are about one minute long. They are often short tricks, like magic and disappearing acts. However, some of the trick films are made by joining several shots together to make an illusion. If you look closely at the film "The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots" (1895), you can see where the shots are joined.

John Taylor was a strong supporter of Republicanism. He was a farmer, and his work and short time in politics made him known for his strong ideas about freedom and government. He believed a farm-based system was the best way to live. This idea influenced his thoughts on the government, its power, and the courts.

Taylor thought the United States had a special chance to create a perfect system. There was no old tradition to follow, so the country's leaders could create a system where people could govern themselves. He believed in the natural rights of people. He thought that if one of these rights is taken away, all the rights are weakened. He believed government should not control these rights. He said that in a natural state, those with physical power and bad intentions often succeed. But in a civilized society, this should not be true.

To create a good society, Taylor thought the government must consider both good and evil in people. He believed in a simple good and evil view of the world. He said government is like people. It has good and bad qualities. He wanted a government that protects private property and helps farmers. He believed a good government would work well even if its leaders are not good. He thought self-interest is a natural part of people, but it is bad when it hurts others. A good government must keep people's natural evil in check.

Taylor wanted a government that follows the Constitution exactly. He wanted a small federal government with only the powers listed in the Constitution. He thought a big government is expensive and might be unfair. He believed a simple interpretation of the Constitution can be bad if it ignores the writers' intentions. He thought the Declaration of Independence is the real charter of the United States because it says the country is a group of states, not one country.

A Look at the Commuter Log Project

There was a big drop in the number of people who used the commuter log in the third month of the project. This was a problem. It is hard to say why this happened. One reason may be the winter weather in New England. Fewer people use their bikes or walk to school when it is cold outside. 

Another reason is that it was the end of the fall semester. Students were busy with schoolwork and final exams. They may have forgotten to use the log. December is also the start of the holiday season. Many students and faculty members do not need to be on campus during this time. When classes started again in January, the number of log submissions did not go up. This was a surprise.

Some people think that any big project will have a lot of energy at the start, but then the interest will decrease. We tried to stop this from happening by creating the Carpool Challenge Week. This was a special event in March to encourage people to use the log again. It helped to increase the number of submissions for that month.

Another problem with the project was that many people like to drive their cars. This is a part of our culture. We tried to make alternative forms of transportation more attractive by giving out prizes. People could win gift cards to local restaurants, coffee shops, and bookstores. We thought this would make them want to use the log. We gave out these prizes for the whole project. 

We thought it would be interesting to see if bigger prizes would help. For example, we could have given away a new bike or a new car. This might have made more people participate. The prizes we gave did not change throughout the project. If the prizes had increased in value, it might have helped to keep people interested.

An ETF, or exchange traded fund, is a security. It is designed to follow a group of things, a product or a group of investments. But it is more flexible and trades like a stock on a stock exchange. An ETF gives you the good things of a group investment and the good things of owning one stock. You can sell more stock than you own, buy some stock with money you borrow, and buy just one share at a time.

ETFs have many benefits. Their costs are lower than the costs of most mutual funds. But there are some bad points too. You have to pay a small fee for every trade like you do for a stock. There are also many different kinds of ETFs to choose from.

It is a good idea to check if the benefits an ETF says it has are true. We will look at the ETF IHF and compare it to its top 10 investments. We want to see if owning one ETF is as good as owning a group of the 10 stocks. We also want to see if we can find a better way to invest in the same stocks.

To make it easier, we will only look at the top 10 investments that make up 63.58% of the ETF. Here are the top 10 investments and their percentage of the total.

To see how well these 10 stocks represent the ETF, we can use a math formula. We will use the current percentage of assets to calculate how much each stock adds to a portfolio's risk and return if the portfolio was made up of only these 10 stocks. The calculations are in the chart below.

From the chart, we can see that a portfolio with only the top 10 stocks makes 6.11% more money than the ETF. It also has a risk level that is 0.12 lower than the ETF. This means that a portfolio of just the top 10 stocks might make more money with less risk. But we need to be sure that these results are real and not just chance.

To do this, we will look at how much each of the top 10 stocks can move up or down. We will then compare these numbers to the ETF's risk level. If the results are different, we can say that the ETF and the portfolio of 10 stocks are not the same.

Edgar Allan Poe's poem "Dream-Land" is one of his famous works. In this poem, Poe uses the word "Thulé" twice. This word comes from the Roman poet Virgil. He used it to describe an island north of Britain. Many people think the Romans used the word to show the edge of the world.

Poe liked the work of German writers. He was very interested in their writing. This is why we think he was influenced by the German writer Goethe. 

Goethe was a famous writer. He wrote a play called "Faust" in two parts. The first part was published in 1808 and the second part was published in 1832, the year he died. In "Faust," there is a short poem called "The King of Thulé." It is about a king who loses his wife. He then drinks a lot and cries because he misses his wife. He decides it is time to die and gives away all his things. He throws a goblet into the sea and dies.

Poe also wrote about Thule in another poem called "The Pit and the Pendulum." He used the word "ultma Thule" in this poem. In "Dream-Land," he uses the word "Thulé" at the beginning and end of the poem. This is interesting because "The King of Thulé" and "Dream-Land" are like companion pieces. In "Dream-Land," the speaker describes a dark and lonely place. He sees a world with no color and is haunted by his dead friends. These scenes are very similar to "The King of Thulé."

Goethe was a famous writer who Poe would have known. Poe liked the work of Alfred Tennyson, and Goethe was also well-known to Tennyson. Poe was exposed to Goethe's work when he read many reproductions of his writing.

California law says a customer who gets hurt from slipping on a spill in a store can get extra money if the store manager knew about the spill but did nothing to clean it up. 

A customer named Jennifer Palmer was hurt after slipping on applesauce in a store called D&D Markets. She wants to prove that the store manager, Paul Martin, acted on purpose to harm her. To win, Palmer must show that Martin knew about the danger and ignored it. 

Martin was told about the spill twice, but he said he was busy eating dinner. Palmer can argue that Martin knew about the danger because many other customers were hurt from slipping in the store before she got hurt. She will say that Martin did not take care of the safety of his store.

Palmer's claim that Martin acted on purpose to harm her is not very strong, but it is possible. Six customers slipped and fell in the store in one year, and Martin did not take action to fix the problem.

On October 13, 2009, Martin was told about the spill twice. He said he was too busy to deal with it. At 5:30 pm, Palmer slipped and fell on the spill and got hurt. Before she got hurt, five other customers slipped and fell in the store.

In California, a person can get extra money if they can prove that someone acted with "oppression, fraud or malice". Malice means acting on purpose to harm someone. If the person did not act on purpose, their behavior must be very bad and they must have been aware of the danger and ignored it.

A court case from many years ago said that someone acts with malice when they ignore the danger and know that it will harm someone. In this case, Martin knew about the danger and ignored it, so a judge may not dismiss Palmer's claim for extra money.

I took a course in Islam at CBC almost four years ago.  One of the main topics we discussed was whether Islam is a hostile religion.  Now this question is even more important than before.  After 9/11, I saw a big change in how the media viewed Islam.  It went from being very critical to being very accepting.  I think it would have been hard for someone like Barack Obama to run for president in 2001.  He has a Muslim background in his family.

I am interested in the Biography of the Prophet.  What I know of the biography does not match the history of Muhammad.  I thought Muhammad forced people to convert to Islam.  But the biography says he was a kind and humble man.  People came to see him because they believed in his teachings.  I also see some similarities between the life of Jesus and the stories of Muhammad.  One story is about Muhammad multiplying food and drink for many people.  This makes me think the writers wanted to show Muhammad as a kind and special person.  This is not fair to Jesus.

There are many stories in the biography about people converting to Islam.  But most of the stories come from other people, not from the people who converted.  This makes me doubt the stories.  The writers also try to make Muhammad seem like a kind and wise man.  But history says he was not kind and humble.  I wonder if Muslims today know the true story of Muhammad's rise to power.

Christianity's early teachings and beliefs are not the same today.  If we look at history, we see that Christianity moved away from its beginnings after Jesus died.  Today, people are becoming more aware and understanding of the past.  They are looking deeper into the true meaning of Christianity.  This will lead to a change in the way people think about their faith.  In the future, many Christians will look back at the teachings added to the religion and compare them to Jesus' original message.  This process will take time, but it is sure to happen.  One day, people will return to Jesus' ideas and throw away the extra teachings that were added over time.  The church will remain strong and lead the way.

This change will make Christianity more alike everywhere.  People will look and believe in the same way.  This is similar to other events in history.  For example, the Roman Empire once persecuted Christians, but later it became Christian.  Our country once had slavery, but now an African-American can be president.  The same thing will happen with Christianity.  People will go back to the beginning and understand Jesus' true message.  This will happen because people will learn to understand Jesus' words as symbols, not as exact statements.

So, what happened to Jesus' teachings?  If we look back in time, we see that the Jewish people were the first to believe in one God.  They believed in a divinely given message and the importance of the Hebrew scriptures.  Before the Romans took control of Jerusalem in sixty-three B.C.E., the Jewish people were divided into different groups.  These groups were the Sadducees, Pharisees, Essenes, Zealots, and many ordinary people.

The book "The Jungle" shows how people are naturally selfish. They only think about themselves and want to make their lives better. The Jungle shows this in many ways. One way is with the owners and managers of big factories. They only want to make their factories bigger and better. They do not care about anyone or anything that gets in their way. They do not care if their pollution hurts people or animals.

The author of the book, Upton Sinclair, says that the factories are making a lot of pollution. This is bad for people and the Earth. The factories are also very dirty. The author says that the owners do not care about the people who work for them. They want to make money, and they do not care about their workers' well-being.

The workers are treated very badly. They have to work long hours, and they are not paid well. The owners can lay them off at any time without giving them help finding a new job. In the past, there were no laws to protect workers. This meant that the owners could do what they wanted. The workers were like slaves. They were very poor and had no way to get help.

The author says that this is not right. He says that workers should be treated fairly and given help when they need it. The book shows how people can be treated unfairly and how they can be forced to live in bad conditions.

Many writers use special techniques to make readers feel a certain way about important subjects. Some of these methods are better than others. F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many of these techniques in his novel The Great Gatsby. 

Fitzgerald pairs words together in new ways to give a special feeling about a subject. He also uses symbols to mean something, and then uses them again to remind readers of that feeling. Fitzgerald uses this method with many colors, like gold, green, white, gray, red, and pink. He builds up a meaning for these colors, and then uses that meaning to create a special feeling about a subject.

Fitzgerald uses the colors white and gray to mean the same thing - uniformity. He thinks white is better and more upper class, while gray is old and faded. He starts to use these colors at the beginning of the novel. Many people wear white: Daisy and Jordan always wear white, Nick wears white clothes to Gatsby's party, and Tom wears a white shirt. Only when Nick is not with the wealthy people is the color white not used.

Fitzgerald also uses white and gray to describe ordinary things. He says the streets of New York are like white chasms, the names of people at Gatsby's party are gray, and Catherine's apartment is just one small part of a long row of white buildings. He uses white and gray to describe regular people or places. 

After Fitzgerald uses these colors enough times, he starts to use them to show readers that something is unimportant or boring. He starts with Daisy. He describes her as wearing white and gray clothes, and readers start to see her as just a regular person, not a special one. Fitzgerald uses this method again to make readers see Daisy as less important. 

Fitzgerald also describes Daisy's fur as gray, and she wears a white dress before Tom and Gatsby's meeting. He uses these colors again to show readers that Daisy is not special, just a regular person.

San Diego County is a good place for farming. The weather is warm and sunny. Many crops grow well here. These include tomatoes, citrus fruits, leafy greens, squash, broccoli, herbs, peaches, lemons, berries, honey, and peppers.

There is a big market for food from local farms. Many people want to buy organic food. This means the food is grown without chemicals. There are many groups in San Diego that support this kind of farming. These groups have long waiting lists.

Some farms also offer tours. People can visit the farms to see how the food is grown. They can also walk or hike in the area. This is fun for people who like the outdoors.

Organic farming is good for the environment. It helps animals and plants. The soil and water are cleaner. However, organic farming can be more expensive. It requires more work to remove pests and weeds. The farmer must also add natural fertilizer to the soil.

The land in this example is near the town of Potrero. It is 160 acres of land with chaparral, grass, and oak trees. The land is next to a national forest. The area has many plants and animals. Some are endangered, like the kangaroo rat and the mountain yellow-legged frog. Others are becoming less common, like the burrowing owl.

This land was once home to Native Americans. Later, people raised cattle and sold wood here. The land was part of a farm a long time ago.

I chose a piece of land from a real estate website. I looked at government programs to see how a small farmer could save money and help the environment. I also found an organic farm in the same area as an example of what might be done with this land.

Culture plays a big role in any negotiation. Culture is not one thing. It can be different in different ways and not the same everywhere. We often make general statements about cultures, like "Russians are stubborn" or "Japanese are accommodating." But these statements are too broad and not true for everyone in a country. Instead of making general statements, it is better to understand what a culture means in a situation and how it can affect talks at the negotiating table. 

When we meet a foreign culture, we see it in a way that is like our own culture, so we make comparisons. To understand a foreign culture, we can learn about its history or its problems. We should not judge or try to change a culture. We should accept it and work within its limits, especially in a negotiation. If we are in a weaker position, showing respect for traditions and values can help us get past cultural differences and move forward.

Culture is not just between countries. Companies have their own cultures too. A company's culture can be seen in how its employees dress, communicate, or do their jobs. Some companies value hard work and long hours, while others have a more relaxed schedule. If we look at American companies, we can see how different they can be from each other. Even within a company, there can be different cultures in different parts of the country or in different cities.

Understanding values is important because they show us why a culture does things. If a culture values saving face or harmony, a negotiator will not publicly criticize their company or boss. If a culture values making a hard bargain, a negotiator will not settle too quickly. Knowing these things can help us negotiate more effectively. We should also try to learn about our opponent on a personal level to make the negotiation successful.

"The fool says, 'There is no God.' This idea is found in the Bible. We will look at two arguments for God's existence. Both come from St. Anselm and Thomas Aquinas. We will compare their ideas.

We will start with the idea that they both believe in the same God. If we do not, we cannot compare their ideas. We will assume they are talking about the same God.

St. Anselm says we can know God exists in our minds. He says we cannot think of a God who does not exist. This means we do not need evidence outside of our minds to understand God. He says we can find truth about God inside ourselves.

St. Thomas Aquinas has a different idea. He says we can prove God's existence with reason and evidence. We do not need faith to understand God. He presents five ideas to support God's existence: change, cause, chance, goodness, and harmony. He says we can know God's existence by thinking about these ideas.

We will look at these ideas to see if one is better than the other."

Long, long ago, a prince was born. He would one day be known as Buddha. This happened in the 500s BC. The prince gave up his life of luxury and became a holy man. He was very wise and his teachings started the religion of Buddhism. There are many kinds of Buddhism, but the most traditional kind is called Theravada Buddhism. This religion is about 2,500 years old. It has changed over time. You can see this in Sri Lanka, a country with many Theravada Buddhists. There, people celebrate the water-cutting ceremony every year. Monks and ordinary people participate in this ceremony. It has some meaning, but Buddha never taught about it.

The Theravada Buddhist community has changed its ideas over time. This happened for many reasons. Some changes came from inside the community. Some came from people outside the community. Some of these changes were good, and some were bad.

There are some important terms to understand. An internal force is a change that comes from people inside the Buddhist community. An external force is a change that comes from people outside the Buddhist community. A hostile force is a change that hurts the Buddhist community. A benign force is a change that does not mean to harm the Buddhist community. These terms will be used often in this discussion.

First, let's look at the basic ideas of Theravada Buddhism. Buddhists believe in three important things: the Buddha, the Dhamma, and the Sangha. The Dhamma is made up of the Tripitaka, a collection of Buddhist books. The Tripitaka has three parts: the Sutta Pitaka, the Vinaya Pitaka, and the Abhidhamma Pitaka. The Sutta Pitaka has the Suttas, which are Buddhist teachings. The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for Buddhist monks and nuns. The Abhidhamma Pitaka has ideas about the nature of reality. These ideas include Anatta (there is no soul), Dukkha (life is suffering), and Anicca (everything is impermanent). When people understand these ideas, they can end the cycle of death and rebirth. They can also end lobha (desire), dosa (hatred), and moha (delusion). This happens when they become enlightened.

The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for how to live. For ordinary people, there are five rules: do not kill, do not lie, do not steal, do not have bad sex, and do not take drugs. For monks and nuns, there are many more rules to follow. The most important idea in Buddhism is the four noble truths. First, life is suffering. Second, desire causes suffering. Third, suffering can be overcome.

The United States and Mexico were once rivals for 57 years. This rivalry lasted from 1836 to 1893. One of the biggest fights between the two countries was the Mexican-American War. The United States won this war in 1846-1848. It got Texas and the American Southwest as new land. Many other fights happened between the two nations. These fights stopped just before World War One.

The two countries had disagreements on many things, including religion and culture. They also had different interests. This is true for many countries that share a border. They often have disagreements that make their relationship difficult.

The United States and Mexico are like other countries that have been rivals with a neighbor. David M. Pletcher said, "Only in Mexico and Cuba did the United States have long-lasting problems." These countries are close to the United States and have been rivals. Other countries in Latin America have good relations with the United States.

Religion was a problem between the two countries. Many countries have had disagreement about religion in the past. One expert said, "If Americans opposed fascism and communism in the 20th century, they opposed Catholicism and monarchy in the 18th and 19th centuries."

These two countries had a distrust of each other. This distrust came from the English and Spanish. They were the colonial rulers of the area. This made it hard for the United States and Mexico to be friends.

The two countries had 17 disagreements during the 57 years of rivalry. Most of these disagreements were about land. The United States and Mexico had problems with bandits and outlaws on their border. They had to use the military to stop these problems.

The rivalry between the two countries began to end when Mexico needed the United States for help. Later, the United States changed its goals from taking land to helping Mexico economically.

Fifteen years ago, I became very sick with an illness I did not know I had. I was a nurse at the time. I chose this job for safety and security. People told me that finding work would always be easy because people are always sick. So, I chose nursing instead of being a scientist or journalist.

But I was 46 years old, single, and had no money. I could not work. I am still sick, and I have been living on disability money for 15 years. I have nothing left that is mine. Every day is hard and makes me feel less safe and less good about myself. I know one thing is true: I would not have made it without the help of my family and friends. They are very kind to me.

I know that bad things happen in life. Some things are too hard to handle by ourselves. We should not depend on the government to help us in hard times. But we should help each other and ask for help when we need it.

Some Americans say we should be independent and strong like our ancestors. But our ancestors did not make it alone. They helped each other and shared what they had.

So, be prepared for emergencies. I have a kit with supplies and a plan. I have food, water, and tools. If you can, grow your own food and be ready for hard times. But also know your neighbors and ask for help when you need it.

Why do living things change over time? Are there limits that affect how they change? 

A long time ago, a scientist named D'Arcy Thompson said that biologists have not yet found a way to explain even simple shapes in scientific language. Today, we still have not solved this problem. However, we are trying to use math to understand how animals develop and change over time.

We are studying a type of animal called Prunum. We want to know how its shell develops and changes over time. We used pictures of the animals to measure the shell's shape and size. We put this information into a computer program to create new, possible shell shapes. These shapes can help us understand how the shell can change.

A shell is like a tube that grows over time. It turns around in a circle, making a spiral shape. This spiral shape is called a whorl. The center of the shell is called the columella. The shell grows in size and makes new whorls over time. Each new whorl is separated from the old one by a line called a suture.

We can look at a shell from different angles. There are four main ways to look at a shell: from the top, from the bottom, from the side, or from the front. When we look at a shell from the front, we see the opening of the shell, called the aperture.

We can count the number of whorls on a shell by looking at it from the top. We draw a line on the shell and count the whorls from that line. We can also look at the path of the opening of the shell as the animal grows. We can use math to describe this path and change the shape of the shell.

By using math to describe how the shell grows, we can change the shape of the shell and understand how it developed. This can help us understand how animals change over time and how they evolve.

Indonesia's health system has a problem. Many babies and young children are dying. This is not getting better. Indonesia wants to meet some of the United Nations' goals by 2015. But it is not making progress in health for babies and mothers.

The number of births where a skilled health worker is present has increased. Now 72% of births have a skilled worker. But many of these workers are not doctors or nurses. They are midwives who cannot help in emergency situations. This means many mothers are still dying from bleeding.

Fewer children are getting medical help for diarrhea. And not enough mothers are getting help after giving birth. This is a big problem.

Doctors are not performing enough operations on pregnant women. Only 4% of women have cesarean sections. But in cities, 7% of women have this operation. In the countryside, it is only 2%. This shows that rich people can get health care, but poor people cannot.

The poor have a hard time getting health care. They have to pay out of their own money. This makes it hard for them to get the help they need.

The question is how to make the health system better. Should Indonesia make special programs for babies and mothers, or should it make the whole health system stronger? Making special programs can help, but it can also cause problems. It can take money away from other areas of health care. And it can make it hard to coordinate services.

Victorian novels are known for their detailed descriptions and focus on the aristocracy.  Two novels that are considered Victorian but are different from this tradition are Oliver Twist and Wuthering Heights.  These novels use mystery and strange situations to make the characters more interesting. This makes it easier for readers to understand their feelings and motives.

A famous example is from the book Oliver Twist. The main character, Oliver, is confused and scared. He hears voices in his head and sees strange things. He is trying to understand what is happening to him. Oliver is talking to two men, Sikes and Crackit, but they are not real. He is still thinking about them even when he is in a different place. Suddenly, he hears a loud noise and sees lights. He is taken away quickly.

In these strange situations, Oliver learns more about himself and the world around him. He finds out about the true nature of things and what is happening to him. Oliver's health is getting worse, and he is having trouble controlling what is happening to him. He is scared and in pain. He does not have control over his life, and this makes him feel defeated.

The same thing happens in Wuthering Heights. The author uses strange and dreamlike situations to make the characters more interesting and to show their feelings and motives. The two novels are different from other Victorian novels because they use mystery and strange situations in a different way.

I worked in an after-school program two years ago. I helped students with their school work, but my strengths were in English and reading. I helped a boy named Adrian. He was having trouble reading. He spoke perfect English, but he had a problem with some letters. This was strange. His mother did not speak English. She spoke Spanish. We used my little Spanish to talk. I understood then that Adrian had trouble with the English alphabet. He could read, but he did not know the alphabet well.

I tell this story to show that a language barrier can be a big problem in school. Even if a student speaks perfect English, reading can still be hard. I think we all agree that this is a problem. What can we do? For Adrian, I helped him with English reading. But for other students who do not speak much English, it is more complicated. There is no simple answer. We need to use many solutions together.

One good idea is a dual language system. This means teaching in two languages, like English and Spanish. This can help all students, not just those who speak Spanish at home. Studies show that students in two-way bilingual programs do better in school. Some people are afraid that this system will waste money and will not help most students. But this is not true. If we use this system in all schools, all students will benefit.

So, how can we do this? Do we need all teachers to speak two languages? No, this is not possible. But we can have special helpers who speak two languages. These helpers can work with teachers to help students who need it. This can help students who do not speak much English.

Most of us learn about something bigger than ourselves when we are young. Some people go to church, others to temple, and some search inside themselves for answers. We learn about the world around us from our parents. But some of us reject what they tell us. We look for our own path in life. We want to understand what is beyond our own world. We look for a light in the dark to guide us.

I asked my father about his favorite bird. We sat on our porch during a rainstorm. He looked out into the rain. He was thin and his hair was thinning. I felt sad and scared. I didn't talk to him about how much I would miss him. I just hugged him and sat with him.

My father died in December when I was 22. He had cancer. He didn't get better even with treatment. I didn't want to watch him die. I wanted to remember him alive, not dead. I knew my father better than anyone. I knew he wouldn't want me to watch him die. I stayed in bed for three days, waiting for news.

Nobody called me.

The Gothic Novel: A New Old Thing

The Gothic Novel is a mix of old and new ideas. Ian Watt calls it an "oxymoron for 'Old-New.'" (Watt) Some people do not like it because it does not have deep meaning. Others praise it for its powerful and exciting qualities. The first Gothic Novel was Horace Walpole's The Castle of Otranto. It used ideas from old romances and modern novels to create a new kind of story. Walpole mixed old and new things to create something new.

The Gothic Novel uses old ideas from the Middle Ages, like theater, architecture, and traditions. People thought the word "Gothic" was old-fashioned. They thought it was not as good as modern ideas. The Gothic Novel combines old and new things in a way that makes it interesting and new for a long time. This is why it has lasted so long.

One important idea in Gothic Novels is chivalry. Chivalry is the idea of training a knight to be brave, honest, and good. The Gothic writers liked this idea because they thought it was missing in their society. They used chivalric ideas to make the past seem better than the present. This was especially true for Horace Walpole, who was writing about a time of trouble. He was unhappy with the way people were behaving. In his Novel, The Castle of Otranto, he created a character named Frederic. Frederic is a good example of a chivalric knight. He is a prince, he has been hurt by bad things, and he is supposed to be a brave and honest man.

Supply chain management is a process that gets goods from customers to products. It includes planning and controlling the flow of goods from raw materials to customers. The term "supply chain management" was first used by consultant Keith Oliver in 1982.

There are six important parts of a supply chain: production, supply, inventory, location, transportation, and information. Business managers use these parts to give good service to customers. 

The first step in the supply chain is production. Production is the base of the supply chain. It decides when, why, where, and how things are made. To know what customers want, managers look at the market. The market tells managers what customers need. 

Managers decide what products to make and how many to make. They also decide where to make the products. They choose a place that can make the products in big numbers and with good quality. They must remember to make sure customers are happy. 

The next step is to plan work and take care of equipment. Production is very important in the supply chain. If every step is not planned, it can cost a company a lot of time and money. 

The second key part of the supply chain is supply. Supply is making good decisions about a company's ability and partnerships. Managers decide which parts of the company can do each job best. They might also send some work to other companies to make things faster and cheaper. This is called outsourcing. It helps a company be flexible and provide good quality at a low cost.

In my past job at Wal-Mart and Target, we had printed books and clear processes for every part of the business. This kept everything running smoothly and helped us know what to do. Having a plan helps a company work well and avoid mistakes.

Hitler is alive in Burma, a sign says. Ellen Page, a famous actress, stands alone on a street corner. She holds a cardboard sign with a scary message. Burma, also known as Myanmar, is a country in Southeast Asia ruled by a bad government. The government took power in 1962 by force. In 2007, people began to protest. These were the first public protests in ten years. The protests were led by many monks. They wore yellow robes. The protests were called the Saffron Revolution. 

At first, the government let the monks have peaceful meetings. But soon, the government became violent. They attacked the monks and the monasteries in the country. They arrested foreign journalists and killed one. A Japanese journalist was killed on September 27th, 2007. He was only there to take pictures of the protest. Many people were killed, but the government only said 13 died. 

This is not new. Governments have been trying to control their people for a long time. In ancient Rome, the emperors thought they were gods. In Japan, the emperors were believed to be gods too. They said they came to Earth to make people's lives better. Our current president had a bad friend, Ted Haggard. He led a group called Stupid People Worldwide.

There have been many bad examples like this. In 1989, many people protested against the Chinese government in Tiananmen Square. The government said 200-300 people died, but other groups said 2,000-3,000 people died. In the 1990s, people in Rwanda were killed because of their ethnic group. This was called a genocide. The Nazis, led by Hitler, also killed many people who were Jewish. This happened in several countries over many years.

Duke Ellington had a great influence on jazz. He lived a long life and had many years to make music. This helped him create many new and interesting pieces. In some of his music, you do not hear him play the piano much. But when he did play, it was usually to help the other musicians. 

Ellington was very good at writing music that showed off what each musician could do. He gave them room to play freely and make up their own music. He also wrote music with many parts that worked together well. This made the orchestra sound new and original.

Ellington knew how to make each musician sound good on their own. He also knew how to make them sound good together. This helped him write some of the most creative and excellent music in jazz history.

The Grove Music dictionary talks about Ellington's music. It says he used the human voice as a special instrument. This was something new and exciting in his time. He did this in many of his songs. 

One of Ellington's early songs, Creole Love Call, is a good example. In this song, the voice is used in a special way. It adds texture and color to the music without using lyrics. This was a new idea at the time.

Creole Love Call is a slow and bluesy song with six parts. Here is what happens in each part:

Part 1: The voice and the woodwind instruments talk to each other in a special way.
Part 2: A trumpet player plays a long and slow solo.
Part 3: A clarinet player plays a fast and high solo with a piano that plays in a special way.
Part 4: The whole band plays the first part again with the brass and woodwind sections talking to each other.
Part 5: The woodwind sections play a fast and high call and response, with the brass and rhythm sections playing in a special way.
Part 6: The song goes back to the first part, but the voice sounds different. It sounds like it is growling like an animal.

The song ends with a short part that has a high-pitched sound and a strange finish by a trombone.

Ellington's use of the voice to add color to his music is a special thing that he did in many of his songs.

In another song, Hot and Bothered, Ellington uses his skill at writing music to make it sound good. He uses a trumpet player and a singer to create a special sound. The singer is not singing words, but using sounds like an instrument. 

In another song, It Don't Mean a Thing (If It Ain't Got That Swing), Ellington uses a trombone player to make the music sound interesting. The trombone player plays a special sound that makes the song sound exciting.

She felt something missing in her life. She did not know what it was. This feeling started when she was 14. She was a teenager. Three years later, at 17, she still felt this way. She thought she wanted a person, but not a boy. She did not like any boy. Some boys liked her, but she did not feel the same way. She wondered why this was happening.

She lived with her parents. They were kind and calm people. They did not argue with each other. They rarely argued with her. They wanted her to be independent.

One day, she was looking for something to do. She walked from room to room. She heard a noise in the kitchen. Her mother was on the ground. She was in pain. "Mom, what's wrong?" her daughter asked. Her mother said, "Ow, I need you to take me to the hospital." Her daughter helped her mother to the car. She drove her to the hospital.

The hospital smelled bad. It was a sad place. But her daughter was not thinking about that. She was worried about her mother. She helped the doctors. They took her mother to a special bed. The daughter sat down and waited.

Her mother fell from a low step while trying to get a vase.

This study wanted to see how eating a "Mediterranean Diet" affects heart disease and stroke. The study showed that eating a diet like this can lower the risk of heart disease and stroke.

The Mediterranean Diet is a special way of eating. It includes a lot of plant foods, like fruits, nuts, whole grains, and vegetables. It also includes fish and small amounts of alcohol. The study used a special score to measure how closely people followed this diet.

Previous studies showed that eating a Mediterranean Diet can be good for you. It can help you lose weight and lower your cholesterol levels. But previous studies did not look at how it affects stroke.

This study looked at 74,886 women from the United States who were between 38 and 63 years old. They did not have heart disease or diabetes. The study followed them for 20 years.

The women were asked every few years about their eating habits. They were asked about the foods they ate and how often they ate them. More than 95% of the women kept participating in the study throughout the 20 years.

The study found that women who ate a Mediterranean Diet had a lower risk of heart disease and stroke. They also had a lower risk of dying from heart disease or stroke. The study controlled for other factors that could affect the results, like smoking and physical activity.

The study showed that eating a Mediterranean Diet can be very good for you. It can lower your risk of heart disease and stroke. This is a good way to eat to stay healthy.

In 2007, the United States had a big financial problem. Many people lost their jobs, and the housing market fell down. Many big companies went out of business. This problem still exists today. We need to ask: how did this happen, and how can we stop it? The problem started because some people in government made bad decisions. They wanted banks and companies to give loans to people who could not pay them back. This was a big mistake because the banks did not have enough money to lend. Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac, two important companies, bought these bad loans and sold them to others. 

This was a bad idea. When people could not pay back their loans, the banks did not have enough money. They sold these bad loans to others, and the problem spread to the whole economy. 

The problem started in 1999. The President at the time, Bill Clinton, wanted to be elected again. He wanted to make people happy, so he changed the rules for lending money. This made it easy to give loans to people who could not pay them back. A news reporter named Steven Holmes wrote in the New York Times in 1999, "Fannie Mae is giving loans to people who cannot pay them back." He said this could cause big problems if there was a crisis. 

Many things combined to make the problem worse. New kinds of loans, like adjustable-rate mortgages, were used. These loans are not good because they can increase the amount of money people owe. Many people in the United States borrowed too much money and bought too many houses. This made the economy very weak. When the housing market fell, many people could not pay their loans. The banks were in trouble. The top five big banks in the United States had a combined debt of $4.1 trillion dollars. This was a big problem. Two banks, Bear Sterns and Merrill Lynch, were sold very cheap. Another bank, Lehman Brothers, went out of business. Some other banks, like Goldman Sachs and Morgan Stanley, had to become commercial banks and follow strict rules. Fannie and Freddie had $5 trillion in debt and were taken over by the government in 2008.

Many writers struggle with exposition.  This is the part of a story where you explain too much.  This can be boring for readers.

You already know the writing tip, "Show, don't tell."  But Dr. Merlin still makes mistakes.  She writes long parts with no action.  This is not what you want.

Exposition is like a devil on your shoulder.  It says, "Get this information out of the way so you can get to the good parts."

Exposition is when you tell the reader what happened.  In a movie, this is like one character talking too much.  In a story, the writer is doing the telling.

A good example is when you read a story and learn about the main character's husband.  You learn that he is a good person and that she loves him very much.  But this does not happen in one or two lines of dialogue.  The writer wants you to like the husband and feel sad when he dies.

So, the writer should show you how much the main character loves her husband.  This can be through what she says and does.  This way, you can feel sad with her when he dies.  You will also learn more about her character.

In short, you want meat on the bone of the story.  You want to learn about the characters and feel what they feel.

As a writer, you need to give your reader that meat.  You should not rush through parts of the story.  You should make the reader want to keep reading.

I watched two news programs from Columbus, Ohio. The first program was "live" from NBC 4 on August 13, 2011. The main story was about a man in Ashley, Ohio who hurt his wife. The man's name was Shad Hostettler. They showed his picture and he looked very bad. They talked about this story for about two minutes because it was still happening.

The second story was about a young man, 18 years old, named Travis Buyers. He was shot in the Sharon Woods area and was very badly hurt. The police had not found anyone to arrest yet. They were investigating. This story was short, but I think it was because the man who was hurt was black. I have noticed that when a black person is a victim of a crime, the news does not talk about it as much. If a white person is a victim, the news talks about it a lot.

The next story was about a hole in a helicopter. They talked about where the helicopter crashed and what kind of bullet hit it. They were asking for help to catch the person who did it. They offered a five-thousand-dollar reward for information.

The news also talked about the weather. They said there would be rain and thunderstorms on Saturday afternoon. The temperature would be in the mid-eighties for the weekend.

They also talked about a store robbery on Clime Road. A black man with a hoodie robbed the store. They said he was about six feet tall and weighed one hundred and fifty pounds. They talked about his skin color a lot.

Another story was about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He was a big drug dealer from Texas. He was convicted of selling a lot of marijuana to people in Ohio from Texas. I noticed they talked about how long he was sentenced to prison, thirty years, instead of saying three hundred months. I don't know why they said it that way. They also said he was Hispanic, but that was not important to the story.

There is a special connection between brothers. This connection is very strong and hard to break. It includes many feelings: love, pride, jealousy, and hurt. Brothers understand each other in a special way. They can see themselves in their brother. In hard times, the true nature of this connection becomes clear. It can be good or bad. The feelings that come from this connection can be very strong. They can also have serious consequences. When one brother sees his brother, he sees himself. He sees the good and the bad. This is where a brother's true character is shown. 

In a story called "The Scarlet Ibis", two brothers show this connection. They have very strong emotions that make them act in different ways. They go on a journey that ends badly. Pride and disappointment mix together in a big way. Only one brother survives. The story shows how the brothers feel about each other. It also shows how their feelings affect their actions.

The older brother's feelings are very important. He wants a brother who can do things with him. He wants someone to play with and have fun with. But his little brother, Doodle, is very sick. He can't do the things the older brother wants him to do. This makes the older brother sad and angry. He even thinks about hurting Doodle. But when Doodle smiles at him, he feels happy. This shows that the older brother loves his brother.

The story is about how brothers feel about each other. It shows how their feelings can be good or bad. It also shows how these feelings can affect their actions.

The human brain is a complex system that processes information. As technology has changed, people have used different ways to describe the brain. Early people compared it to a flat piece of wax, then to a piece of paper, and now to a computer. These comparisons are helpful, but they have limits.

The brain takes in information from the senses. These include touch, heat, sound, and light. The brain changes this information into electrical signals. It does this again and again in two processes: bottom-up and top-down.

Imagine looking at a picture of a black box. Bottom-up processing puts together simple information like color and shape. It helps you see the box. Top-down processing uses this information to help you identify the box. It helps you understand what it is.

The brain has a filter that decides what is important and what to focus on. For example, when you look at the ground, your brain does not notice individual blades of grass. But it can hear your name even in a noisy room.

The brain stores information and uses it again later. There are three kinds of memory: short-term, working memory, and long-term. Information is first encoded, or put into the brain. There are different ways to encode different kinds of information. For example, written words can be encoded based on how they look, how they sound, or what they mean.

The brain keeps information in different ways. Working memory holds information for a short time, about 20 seconds. Long-term memory is stored in the structure of special kinds of proteins.

Scientists have many different ideas about how the brain organizes knowledge. Some are based on how people remember things, others on how computers work, and others on how the brain works. One idea is that the brain is like a network of connected nodes, or points. Each node represents a concept, and they are connected based on how they are related. For example, the word "chair" might be connected to "table," which is connected to "wood."

Aldous Huxley writes about a bad future in his book Brave New World. He criticizes the way people will live under a system controlled by technology and capitalism. The people in the book value being with friends above being an individual. They are taught from a young age to be happy now, not to think about the future. The citizens are like pawns in a game. They must do what the World Controller says. By looking at the book from a Marxist point of view, we can see that Huxley did not like the way capitalism was growing at that time.

Huxley criticizes capitalism by showing how people are not free to make their own choices. They are forced to buy things they do not need and to work hard to get more things. The people in the book, like the Delta and Gamma classes, do not have the power to make choices. They are controlled by the World Controller. He makes them want to buy and use things. This is like the idea of false consciousness in Marxism. The people do not know how the system works, and they are not free.

The people in the book do not have real relationships with each other. They are not allowed to feel deep emotions like love or happiness. They only care about how they look and what they have. The way people interact with each other in the book shows that they are not free to be themselves. They are like robots, doing what they are told.

The people in the book are happy to be in their place in society. They do not want to change. This is like the idea of the proletariat in Marxism. The people are controlled by the system, and they are happy to be controlled. They are not aware of how the system works, and they do not want to know.

I have been a student at University Park for two and a half years. Getting around campus can be difficult. My freshman year, I lived in East Halls, which is on the far side of campus. Going to classes in buildings like Willard, near the center, took 25 minutes on foot. The weather was often bad, so it took even longer. I talked to a graduate who said that not long ago, East Halls was far from other buildings. Now it is surrounded by sports fields, new buildings, and apartments.

As campus grows, getting around becomes harder. One good solution is a bicycle. But students need to ride them and the campus needs to be good for bicyclists. My friend recently started riding again. He said, "Bikes are great. It's the only way to get around." Bicycling is also good for your body. It's the best way to travel on campus. I live off campus, near Thomas building. My bike takes me there in 5 minutes. The road to Thomas is not always easy to ride on. Walking is also good, but I am too busy. If I didn't have a bike, I would have to walk, which would take 30-40 minutes. That is 2 1/2 hours a week. I don't have that much time.
